n_team\", \"score\": 0.8594857339039801, \"rank\": 0.13453763796990073, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9330050222517822, \"rank\": 0.07179338436681988, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first-ever Olympic women's breakdancing competition\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"no points\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"all three matches\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"her pool\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old's bizarre dancing - which included hopping around like a kangaroo and doing the 'sprinkler' - made waves across the world, quickly becoming a global meme.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 36-year-old's bizarre dancing\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"a kangaroo\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'sprinkler' - made waves\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"a global meme\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's father-in-law Andrew Free has hit back at the scores of the judges, suggesting she did not make it through to the finals because it was a \\\"pretty stacked competition\\\" and judges were \\\"looking for a certain style of breaking which is not Rachael's\\\".\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9998889730710107, \"rank\": 0.0001110392570456835, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"law\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 709}, {\"ngram\": \"the scores\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"pretty stacked competition\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"judges\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain style\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although they are supposed to mark 5 different aspects with each having the same weighting, in my obviously biased opinion they did not reward originality and musicality so she was up against it,\\\" Mr Free said on Facebook.\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"5 different aspects\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"the same weighting\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"my obviously biased opinion\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"originality\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"musicality\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Free\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"Facebook\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The main thing is she represented Australia and breaking at the Olympics with courage and dignity.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9364551010457252, \"rank\": 0.04452264685367256, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The main thing\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"dignity\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It comes naturally for some of them, not so much for Rachael.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9998889730710107, \"rank\": 0.0001110392570456835, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is part of the culture.\\\"\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head breaking judge at the Olympics, Martin Gilian, said the scores of zero were not indicative of a terrible performance.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1401, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.999999998138037, \"rank\": 1.712869449059693e-09, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Head breaking judge\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"the scores\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"a terrible performance\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all about originality and it's all about bringing something new to the table and representing your country or region,\\\" Mr Gilian said, according to CNN.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9999999999497504, \"rank\": 5.020421624114356e-11, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"originality\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"your country\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"region\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Gilian\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is exactly what Raygun was doing, she got inspired by her surroundings, which in this case, for example, was a kangaroo\\u2026 she created some original moves which could be maybe funny or entertaining for others, but for us, she basically represented breaking and hip hop.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6689596581017106e-25, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her surroundings\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1757}, {\"ngram\": \"a kangaroo\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"some original moves\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1860}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"hip hop\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was trying to be original and bring something new to the table.\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From our perspective, that was nothing really shocking.\\\"\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our perspective\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it has been the subject of relentless mocking on social media, Gunn's performance at the Olympics has also been shrouded in controversy.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2119, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9807940700527122, \"rank\": 0.01958126059708914, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the subject\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2079}, {\"ngram\": \"relentless mocking\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, who has a PhD in breakdancing and dance culture and works as a lecturer at Macquarie University, was accused of getting zero points on purpose for an academic study.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2194, \"end\": 2198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9807940700527122, \"rank\": 0.01958126059708914, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.355770101898467e-22, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}], \"noun_phrase