le, who admitted she and her friends were \\\"s***ting ourselves laughing for nearly 24 hours\\\" after watching the event.\", \"from\": 3368, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3423, \"end\": 3428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adele\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.205148249934388e-16, \"text\": \"Adele\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adele\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adele\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recent concert\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"her friends\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3462}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 24 hours\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout Our Apps\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 3553, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"pleaselog\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3580}, {\"ngram\": \"an account?Register\", \"from\": 3596, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3637}, {\"ngram\": \"Our Apps\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3675}]}]}"